com.googlecode.cqengine.query.option

Class Thresholds

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.googlecode.cqengine.query.option.Thresholds

  • public class Thresholds
extends Object
    A wrapper around Thresholds which have been set into query options.

    Example usage using QueryFactory:
    QueryOptions queryOptions = queryOptions(applyThresholds(INDEX_ORDERING_SELECTIVITY, 0.4))

    Author:
    niall.gallagher
